      mpmset $n quest 0 4 1
      smile $n
      say Greetings $N.
      say I've been waiting for an adventurer like you to arrive!
      say Our mining goes well, but my latest creation is lacking a centerpiece jewel.
      mpdelay self 14 1 $n
